 und kultursensible Behandlungsansätze gestärkt werden müssen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aDepression in womenxSocial aspects. 0aWomenxMental healthxCross-cultural studies. 4aEthnologie. 4aFrauen. 4aGender Studies. 4aGender. 4aKultur. 4aPsychoanalyse. 4aPsychologie. 4aSüdländer. 7aPSYCHOLOGY / Movements / Psychoanalysis.2bisacsh  aCulture.  aEthnology.  aGender Studies.  aGender.  aPsychology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Sozialw. 2000-2009z9783110463392oZDB-23-TSW0 cprintz978389942435540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839404355?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839404355423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839404355/original  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2000d2009  aZDB-23-TSWc2000d2009